pullRequest.body:
This is in preparation for a linter that will enforce `assert_not_exists`s to be placed right after the initial doc-module strings.

I also guarded against the downstream-existing `ModuleCat.abelian`, instead of the nowhere-existing `Module.abelian`.

---

- [x] depends on: #15715
